(39, 2, 0, 2, 11, 0, 'Medical Officer', 0, 0, 'â¢	Contributing clinical expertise to patient care and providing guidance to junior physicians.\r\nâ¢	Performing administrative duties and risk management.\r\nâ¢	Ensuring the highest standards in patient care is maintained.\r\nâ¢	Verifying complex diagnoses and facilitating treatment plans.\r\nâ¢	During rounds assist consultants.\r\nâ¢	Managing allocated budgets and identifying areas of improvement in inpatient care.\r\nâ¢	Ensuring compliance with healthcare regulations and safety standards.\r\nâ¢	Reporting to Senior Consultants, as well as liaising between administrative and medical staff.\r\nâ¢	Ensuring consistent and accurate medical recordkeeping practices.\r\n\r\n', 'â¢	Contributing clinical expertise to patient care and providing guidance to junior physicians.\r\nâ¢	Performing administrative duties and risk management.\r\nâ¢	Ensuring the highest standards in patient care is maintained.\r\nâ¢	Verifying complex diagnoses and facilitating treatment plans.\r\nâ¢	During rounds assist consultants.\r\nâ¢	Managing allocated budgets and identifying areas of improvement in inpatient care.\r\nâ¢	Ensuring compliance with healthcare regulations and safety standards.\r\nâ¢	Reporting to Senior Consultants, as well as liaising between administrative and medical staff.\r\nâ¢	Ensuring consistent and accurate medical recordkeeping practices.\r\n\r\n', 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0),
