(62, 2, 0, 0, 18, 0, 'HR Executive ', 0, 0, '1.	To Maintain personnel file record, scanning and uploading of documents.\r\n2.	Conduct interviews and fill interview sheets.\r\n3.	Taking care of all employees ,leave record of employees.\r\n4.	Prepare and complete Face Sheet of new joinee. \r\n5.	Conduct and ensure that all new joiners undergo induction training.\r\n6.	Proper maintenance & completion of all old and new record.\r\n7.	Prepare daily Checklist.\r\n8.	Late punch (LP) and Miss punch (MP) detail record.\r\n9.	Issue Locker, Access Card and ID cards.\r\n10. Bio-metric Verification.\r\n11. Birthday Intimation.\r\n12. Prepare list of Pre-health check up and Annual health check up.\r\n13. Issue of Offer, Appointment letter to the staff.\r\n14. Maintaining and keeping employee Resignation letters and information.\r\n', '1.	To Maintain personnel file record, scanning and uploading of documents.\r\n2.	Conduct interviews and fill interview sheets.\r\n3.	Taking care of all employees ,leave record of employees.\r\n4.	Prepare and complete Face Sheet of new joinee. \r\n5.	Conduct and ensure that all new joiners undergo induction training.\r\n6.	Proper maintenance & completion of all old and new record.\r\n7.	Prepare daily Checklist.\r\n8.	Late punch (LP) and Miss punch (MP) detail record.\r\n9.	Issue Locker, Access Card and ID cards.\r\n10. Bio-metric Verification.\r\n11. Birthday Intimation.\r\n12. Prepare list of Pre-health check up and Annual health check up.\r\n13. Issue of Offer, Appointment letter to the staff.\r\n14. Maintaining and keeping employee Resignation letters and information.\r\n', 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0),
