(64, 2, 0, 0, 20, 0, 'BIO- Medical Engineer', 0, 0, '1. Ensure that Medical Inventory is Complete and Labeling done. \r\n2 Prepare Master list of all equipments. \r\n3. Provided manuals are collected and arranged.  \r\n4. Daily maintenance round in all departments. \r\n5. To arrange provided documents in respective files\r\n6. Co-ordinate with vendors and conducted Preventive maintenance certificates \r\n7. Equipments that are malfunctioned or need repair are enlisted\r\n8. List of equipments / accessories is prepared that are in shortage in hospital\r\n9. Preventive maintenance schedules started for varies equipments in all departments. \r\n10. List of equipment under warranty is prepared\r\n11. List of equipment under AMC/CMC is prepared\r\n12. Future perspective is to start staff induction for proper handling and operation of equipments\r\n13. To provide/issue medical inventory to various departments as fixed assets.\r\n14.  Equipment Break down record \r\n15.  Provides training to staff at the time of installation of new equipment. \r\n\r\n', '1. Ensure that Medical Inventory is Complete and Labeling done. \r\n2 Prepare Master list of all equipments. \r\n3. Provided manuals are collected and arranged.  \r\n4. Daily maintenance round in all departments. \r\n5. To arrange provided documents in respective files\r\n6. Co-ordinate with vendors and conducted Preventive maintenance certificates \r\n7. Equipments that are malfunctioned or need repair are enlisted\r\n8. List of equipments / accessories is prepared that are in shortage in hospital\r\n9. Preventive maintenance schedules started for varies equipments in all departments. \r\n10. List of equipment under warranty is prepared\r\n11. List of equipment under AMC/CMC is prepared\r\n12. Future perspective is to start staff induction for proper handling and operation of equipments\r\n13. To provide/issue medical inventory to various departments as fixed assets.\r\n14.  Equipment Break down record \r\n15.  Provides training to staff at the time of installation of new equipment. \r\n\r\n', 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0),
(65, 2, 0, 0, 21, 0, 'Accounts Incharge', 0, 0, 'â¢	Supervision of all accounts assistant\r\nâ¢	Handling all accounts of the hospital\r\nâ¢	Tax compliances (TDS/Advance tax/Balance sheet)\r\nâ¢	Handling Cheques\r\nâ¢	Verifying bills and vouchers\r\nâ¢	Handling Drn Naveen Account \r\nâ¢	Handling bank compliance(Neft/Transactions/DD)\r\nâ¢	Handling financials of marketing department\r\n\r\n', 'â¢	Supervision of all accounts assistant\r\nâ¢	Handling all accounts of the hospital\r\nâ¢	Tax compliances (TDS/Advance tax/Balance sheet)\r\nâ¢	Handling Cheques\r\nâ¢	Verifying bills and vouchers\r\nâ¢	Handling Drn Naveen Account \r\nâ¢	Handling bank compliance(Neft/Transactions/DD)\r\nâ¢	Handling financials of marketing department\r\n\r\n', 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0),
